## 3. Sequence Diagram (Normal Operation Loop)

This diagram shows the **Non-Blocking Capture** flow designed to prevent GStreamer crashes.

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant Cam as GStreamerCamera
    participant Cap as Capture Thread
    participant PQueue as Processing Queue
    participant Proc as Processing Thread
    participant AI as AI Thread

    loop Capture Loop
        Cap->>Cam: read(raw_frame)
        Cam-->>Cap: Frame Buffer
        Cap->>Cap: clone() & release(raw_frame)
        Cap->>PQueue: push(work_frame)
    end

    loop Processing Loop
        PQueue->>Proc: wait_and_pop()
        Proc->>Proc: Enhance & Save to Buffer
        Note over Proc, AI: 1 FPS Interval Check
        Proc->>AI: push(clone)
        Proc->>Proc: Network Write & Display
    end

    loop AI Loop
        AI->>AI: detect()
        AI->>Proc: Update shared_result
    end
```

