## 6. Recommendations for Further Optimization

1.  **Zero-Copy AI Interface**: Currently, OpenCV `Mat` is converted to TFLite tensors in [ImagePreprocessor](file:///c:/Users/1-05/Downloads/SubCameraApp_refactory_260311/SubCameraApp_refactory_260311/src/imageprocessing/ImagePreprocessor.cpp#4-15). Explore using DMABUF directly in TFLite if the model supports it.
2.  **SIMD Acceleration**: The `AdvancedEnhancers` (e.g., LowLight) use pixel-level loops. These can be accelerated using **ARM NEON Intrinsics**.
3.  **Static Result Memory**: Pre-allocate [DetectionResult](file:///c:/Users/1-05/Downloads/SubCameraApp_refactory_260311/SubCameraApp_refactory_260311/src/ai/IAiDetector.h#18-22) buffers to avoid `std::vector` heap allocations in the high-frequency loop.
4.  **Network-Adaptive Bitrate**: Add a telemetry feedback loop to adjust the GStreamer `video_bitrate` dynamically when network packet loss is detected by `udpsink`.

